text:
What do the public spats between House Dems mean for a Biden administration?

It’s not strange for parties to reconfigure and have family fights after an election. But with what could be a slim majority in the House next year, every little fight matters https://t.co/M5yb0j1dW6 https://t.co/xdvSkuO4Kx

text:
